Package org.usfirst.frc.team3926.robot.commands.Gears

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CenterOnGears
    Centers the robot on the vision target for gear placement
    DriveToGears
    Drive towards the gear placement vision target
    GearPlacementMotorDown
    Puts the gear placement system's motor down (blocking the gear from falling out)
    GearPlacementMotorUp
    Puts the gear placement system's motor up (letting the gear come out)
